{
  "metadata": {
    "title": "Factor of Safety Calculation for Shaft",
    "subject": "Machine Design",
    "documentType": "problem-set"
  },
  "pages": [
    {
      "pageIndex": 0,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Ques A rotating shaft of 16 mm diameter is subjected to an axial load 5000 N. Steady torque 50 Nm and maximum bending moment of 75 Nm. Calculate the probable factors of safety using maximum normal stress theory and maximum shear stress theory by taking the limiting strength of shaft material as 400 MPa."
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Solution="
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Shaft diameter = 16 mm"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Axial load = 5000 N"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Torque = 50 Nm = $50 \\times 10^3$ N.mm"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Bending Moment = $75 \\times 10^2$ N.mm"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "$\\sigma_y$ = 400 MPa = $400 \\times 10^6$ N/$m^2$ = 400 N/$mm^2$"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "theories: I, II"
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\sigma_1 = \\frac{\\sigma}{2} + \\frac{1}{2}\\sqrt{\\sigma^2 + 4\\tau^2}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "M = \\frac{\\pi}{32} \\sigma_{bending} d^3",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\sigma_{axial} = \\frac{\\text{load}}{A}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "= \\frac{5000}{\\frac{\\pi}{4} d^2}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "= \\frac{5000}{\\frac{\\pi}{4} (16)^2}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "= 24.867 \\text{ N/mm}^2",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\sigma_{bending} = \\frac{32M}{\\pi d^3}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "= \\frac{32 \\times 75 \\times 10^3}{\\pi (16)^3}",
          "display": true
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "= 186.50 \\text{ N/mm}^2",
          "display": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}